ent from the conventional jet energy loss models. The current study can,\ntherefore, provide important new insights on mechanisms regarding the modeling\nof the medium and hard-soft interactions in heavy ion collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 18:45:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
