mated, and\nthus it can be of great benefit for the comprehensive self-consistent modelling\nframeworks that are attempting to simulate complex events such as tokamak\nstart-up or disruptions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 19:49:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2021 17:44:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2021 18:16:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 27 May 2021 11:24:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-28"}
