. We also compute the nucleus size to be in\nthe range $0.18\\leq r \\leq 3.1$ Km. Our observations show that 2I/Borisov's\nbehaviour is analogous to that of the Solar system comets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 20:23:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
