tic dense environment; a fraction that is\nsimilar to previous studies. The spectroscopic redshift is known for 15 of\nthese 31 sources, thus this photometric approach is tested using spectroscopy.\nWe are able to confirm that 7 out of 15 SMGs lie in high-density peaks.\nHowever, the search for associated extended X-ray emission via an X-ray\nstacking analysis leads to a detection that is not statistically significant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2021 12:09:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-24"}
